exportmetadata: 06-11-2020 version includes new spatial and tabular data.  Removed map unit Sb.  (Sb was combined with Sac3AF.)  Includes completely new tabular data for HkB.  Map unit names for Gn, HkA, and Sac3AF were changed, and these map units also include completely new tabular data.  Includes minor edits to other map units.  Includes edits to some interpretations.
